URL: https://github.com/cmu-delphi/covidcast
Description: Tools for building COVID-19 statistical models, with an emphasis on
    short-term forecasting and hotspot prediction. This package is meant to be 
    used in conjuction with the `covidcast` and `evalcast` <tt>R</tt> packages 
    developed by the Delphi research group headquartered at Carnegie Mellon 
    University.
